snippet.title: Grow Flow - Announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Grow Flow is a parkour platforming game about growing and shrinking cubes to make your way through the levels.

Grow Flow contains:
- Over 60 levels, divided between 7 chapters!
- In-game save system!
- Fully voice-acted goddess!
- Hidden and optional mechanics!
- Beautiful soundtrack!
- Secrets?

Grow Flow will be launching Q1 2022!

Follow us on Twitter for updates!
https://twitter.com/Virus0Team

#GrowFlow
